    G D M  SYNTAX DESCRIPTION

    Structuring a project is optimally supported by the SYMBOLIC
    REPRESENTATION of the project sources and parameters.
    The division into different layers allows for a birds eye view of multi-
    processor projects.
    

    @374[< GDM Layers         >]     - PCC Layer, Processor Layer, Task Layer


    @378[< GDM Objects        >]     - Objects for different layers
                               - Data Branch


    @371[< GDM Basics         >]     - Explanation of the basics





