      Indicates a BR module (e.g.: Bugfix, Runtime module of the libraris,
      exception handler etc.). After this object has been inserted, a POP-UP
      menu with a list of all system modules which are installed in the system
      but which are not entered in the GDM, appears. After selecting a list
      entry, the respective BR module is copied to the module directory of the
      current CPU (or processor).

