    <LABEL FIELD   >:The LABEL NAME is followed by a ":" and is the first
                     item on the line. Labels are optional and can be the
                     only item on the line.

    <OPERATOR FIELD>:An OPERATOR can be either a KEY WORD (STL command) 
                     or a FUNCTION NAME.

    <OPERAND FIELD>: An operator can have ONE or MORE OPERANDS.
                     Basic operations can only have one operand.

    <COMMENT FIELD> :Comments are enclosed between "(*" and "*)". They are
                     allowed anywhere that spaces are allowed (also between
                     fields). Comments are not allowed to continue without
                     having a new "(*" and "*)" on every line.


