    L A D  -  SYNTAX DESCRIPTION

    The advantage of symbolic programming in the LADDER DIAGRAM editor is the
    ability to get a good overview of the program flow and the logical links.
    I/O assignments can easily be made using the various contact objects, inputs
    and outputs (analog or digital).

    
