       - The input or output at the current cursor position is highlighted.
         After the cursor has been positioned, the connection can be moved to
         the new FREE POSITION, by pressing <ENTER> or with a MOUSE click.
       - Inputs are always located on the left, and outputs are always on the
         right-hand side of an FBK.


