    - <HOME> and <END> moves the cursor to the start or end of the string.
    - <BACKSPACE> deletes the last digit of a number.
    - <ENTER> completes and confirms the entry and the cursor is moved to
      the next field in the dialog box.

    <INPUT FIELD with Pop-Up Selection Window>
    - Indication: There is a '' on the left hand side of the input field.
    - With almost any entry, a POP-UP WINDOW is opened and various
      possibilities are listed.
      - The desired entry can be selected with the <CURSOR> keys or via
        the STARTING LETTER.
      - The selected entry of the pop-up window is confirmed and displayed
        in the dialog box, when <ENTER> is pressed, or a mouse click 
        is carried out.



